				<title>Foundation Cool Achievement Badges</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/dark-achievement-badges</link>
				<description>

&lt;div style=&quot;display: none&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;by &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610162277&quot; alt=&quot;EstrellaYoshte&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte&quot;  &gt;EstrellaYoshte&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 18 Dec 2020 04:58:41 +0000</pubDate>
												<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="display: none"></div> <div class="creditRate"> <div class="rateBox"> <div class="rate-box-with-credit-button"> <div class="creditButton"> <p><a class="fa fa-info" href="#u-credit-view"></a></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div style="clear:both;"></div> <div id="u-credit-view"> <div class="fader"> <p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style=""></iframe></p> </div> <div class="modalcontainer"> <div class="modalbox"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>Info</span></h2> </div> <hr /> <div class="credit first"> <p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/5" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p> <p>Component Page: <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:sybadge">http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:sybadge</a><br /> Foundation Cool Achievement Badges by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610162277" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span></p> </div> <hr /> <div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;"> <p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p> </div> <div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;"> <div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>Borrowing the words of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610162277" alt="RJB_R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" >RJB_R</a></span>:</p> <blockquote> <p><em>This is a just-for-fun type of page for people to list their accomplishments and provide badges for display on their author pages.</em></p> </blockquote> <p>The primary goal of this page is a visually neat way to showcase user's achievements, as well as to encourage community engagement. All the badges below aim to be as vote-independent as possible.</p> <p>Since I can not enforce the requirements for these, this will based on an honor system, in which I hope everyone strives to give their best shot, and remembers to have fun!</p> <hr /> <div class="anchor"> <div class="sidebox" style="padding: 10px;"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h3><span>Achievements Unlocked</span></h3> <h5><span>(out of <span style="color: #cea0ff">16</span>)</span></h5> </div> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/estrellayoshte">EstrellaYoshte</a> - 2<br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/ihp-s-author-page">Ihp</a> - 5<br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/jakdragonx-rage-collection">JakdragonX</a> - 3<br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/this-page-intentionally-left-blank">HarryBlank</a> - 3<br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/yossipossi-authorphage">Yossipossi</a> - 5<br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/researcher-nyka-s-file">Nykacolaquantum</a> - 2<br /> <a href="http://scp-wiki-de.wikidot.com/dr-rabes-personalakte">Einer von Rabe</a> - 6</p> </div> </div> <div class="casercontainer"> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>TSF</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/tsf.png" width="160px" alt="tsf.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Ten Steps Forward</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Have 10 pages published on the wiki.<br /> (Fragment pages do not count, if you're wondering.)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>MWW</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/mww.png" width="160px" alt="mww.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Dr. Worldwide</span></h1> <hr /> <p>A work of yours is translated to 5 or more foreign languages, OR you have translated 6 works from one language to another.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CCC</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/ccc.png" width="160px" alt="ccc.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Canon Crossover Central</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Write an article involving 3 (or more) canons. Tales series and other incorporated settings with dedicated hubs are permitted for the purpose of this achievement.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>SEK</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/sek.png" width="160px" alt="sek.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>The SEXTANK Initiative</span></h1> <hr /> <p>You have written: <strong>S</strong>afe, <strong>E</strong>uclid, <strong>K</strong>eter, <strong>T</strong>haumiel, <strong>N</strong>eutralized, E<strong>x</strong>plained + <strong>A</strong>nother Esoteric-class.<br /> (The absence of Object Class altogether does not qualify as esoteric.)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>SCL</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/scl.png" width="160px" alt="scl.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Social Butterfly</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Leave detailed and constructive critique in the comments 20 times.<br /> Use your judgement as to what qualifies as detailed and constructive. Ideas and draft critiques also count.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CLB</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/clb.png" width="160px" alt="clb.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Thank You for Your Cooperation</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Collaborate with at least 7 other authors.<br /> This could be 7 different co-authored pages or one co-authored page with your 7 co-authors, and everything in-between (You must be credited as a co-author to qualify.)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>DDA</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/dda.png" width="160px" alt="dda.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Double Double Agent</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Write 4 or more distinct GoI Formats (at least one article for each four GoIs.)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>GSA</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/gsa.png" width="160px" alt="gsa.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Guest Star Appearance</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Write an article featuring an SCP, GoI, character or other major elements originating from a foreign branch (Bonus points if it's an obscure one!)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>TLT</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/tlt.png" width="160px" alt="tlt.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Tall Tales</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Have 10 tales published on the wiki. Parts of a bigger story count, as long as they're separate pages.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>TBE</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/tbe.png" width="160px" alt="tbe.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Team Building Exercise</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Write an article featuring two (or more) characters or GoIs who would never work together/has seldom even met deciding to cooperate for once. Bonus points if it doesn't involve the Foundation in any way.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CHL</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/chl.png" width="160px" alt="chl.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>The Challenger</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Complete at least three challenges on the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/writing-challenge-list">Writing Challenges List</a>.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>STR</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/str.png" width="160px" alt="str.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Making Strides</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Have 50 pages published on the wiki.<br /> (Fragment pages still don't count, ha.)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>AWB</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/awb.png" width="160px" alt="awb.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Are We the Baddies?</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Write an article where the Foundation is explicitly an antagonistic force.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CTS</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/cts.png" width="160px" alt="cts.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>The Centurion</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Have 100 pages published on the wiki. Whoa!<br /> (You're pretty awesome, you know that?)</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>PBS</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/pbs.png" width="160px" alt="pbs.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Playing for both Sites</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Be an author of both the SCP Wiki and the <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/">Wanderer's Library</a>.</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>SPA</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/spa.png" width="160px" alt="spa.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>Student Participation Award</span></h1> <hr /> <p>Attend two site-hosted Workshops or Seminars. Bonus points if you publish an article utilizing your newly acquired knowledge!</p> </div> </div> <hr /> <p>To have the badges on your page, put the following in:</p> <div class="darkbox" style="font-family: monospace;"> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[=]]</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:sybadge&#32;code=aaa]]</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:sybadge&#32;code=bbb]]</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/=]]</span></p> </div> <br /> In place of <em>aaa</em> and <em>bbb</em>, use the three-letter key at the top left of the card corresponding to your chosen badge (all lowercase). <div style="text-align: center;"><span class="tooltip"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dark-achievement-badges"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/sek.png" style="background-color: var(--bgBadgeColor); padding: .66rem .7rem .4rem .5rem; border-radius: .6rem 2.5rem .6rem .6rem; margin: .3rem; border: solid 4px var(--borderColor);" width="64px" alt="sek.png" class="image" /></a><span class="tooltiptext"><span class="sek"> </span></span></span><span class="tooltip"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dark-achievement-badges"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/scl.png" style="background-color: var(--bgBadgeColor); padding: .66rem .7rem .4rem .5rem; border-radius: .6rem 2.5rem .6rem .6rem; margin: .3rem; border: solid 4px var(--borderColor);" width="64px" alt="scl.png" class="image" /></a><span class="tooltiptext"><span class="scl"> </span></span></span></div> <p>To change the color of the badge border and background, put the following:</p> <div class="darkbox" style="font-family: monospace;"> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[module&#32;CSS]]</span><br /> :root {<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;--borderColor:&#32;(COLOR&#32;HERE)&#32;!important;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;--bgBadgeColor:&#32;(COLOR&#32;HERE)&#32;!important;</span><br /> }<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/module]]</span></p> </div> <p>By default, the colors are #CEA0FF and #21252E, respectively.</p> <hr /> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <h1><span>Got an idea for one?</span></h1> <p>This page will continue to be updated with new achievements.<br /> If you think there's something that needs to be added, leave a comment! I'll do my best to accommodate them!</p> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610162277" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span></p> 
