&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Who Framed Ralph Roget?&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Don&#039;t ask if the title came first. You know the answer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/this-page-intentionally-left-blank/WhoFramed.png&quot; alt=&quot;WhoFramed.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scp-wiki.net/this-page-intentionally-left-blank&quot;&gt;More by this author!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
