w.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead&quot;  &gt;The Pighead&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;General George Bowe has been dead for a long time. As dead as he can be, in his condition. But he&#039;s tired of being dead, and he&#039;s got a job to do.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
