by &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5379342&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610162281&quot; alt=&quot;redredred&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5379342)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred&quot;  &gt;redredred&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610162281&quot; alt=&quot;Nagiros&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros&quot;  &gt;Nagiros&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610162281&quot; alt=&quot;Calibri Bold&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold&quot;  &gt;Calibri Bold&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, and &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610162281&quot; alt=&quot;Grigori Karpin&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin&quot;  &gt;Grigori Karpin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Director Sophia Light is in a precarious position as an anomaly beneath a Site in Yellowstone has begun to wake up.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
